{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "sanrio-coffee-api-collection",
    "name": "SanrioCoffee API",
    "description": "三麗鷗咖啡線上點餐平台 API 測試 Collection\n\n**建議測試順序：**\n1. Auth → Register Admin → Login Admin（存 admin_token）\n2. Auth → Register Consumer → Login Consumer（存 token）\n3. [Admin] 分類 → 建立分類（存 category_id）\n4. [Admin] 商品 → 建立商品 → 新增客製化選項\n5. [Consumer] 購物車 → 加入商品\n6. [Admin] 優惠券 → 建立優惠券\n7. [Consumer] 點餐 → 驗證優惠券 → 建立訂單（存 order_id）\n8. [付款] 發起付款 → 模擬成功回調\n9. [Admin] 訂單管理 → 推進狀態\n10. [Consumer] 點數 → 查看點數歷程",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",     "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "admin_token",  "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token",        "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Consumer token，由 Login Consumer 自動填入" },
    { "key": "category_id",  "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "product_id",   "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "option_id",    "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "cart_item_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "order_id",     "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "transaction_id","value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "coupon_id",    "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "coupon_code",  "value": "WELCOME10", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "註冊、登入、查看當前使用者。Login 會自動將 token 存入 collection variable。",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"sanrio_admin\",\n  \"email\": \"admin@sanriocoffee.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"phone\": \"0912345678\",\n  \"role\": \"admin\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register (Consumer)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"kitty_fan\",\n  \"email\": \"kitty@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"phone\": \"0987654321\",\n  \"role\": \"consumer\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('admin_token', json.data.token);",
                  "    console.log('[Admin] token saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@sanriocoffee.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Consumer)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "    console.log('[Consumer] token saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"kitty@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (當前使用者)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","me"] }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "[公開] 商品目錄",
      "description": "不需要 token 的公開查詢端點。",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Categories",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/categories", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","categories"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List Products (全部)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api","v1","products"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List Products (上架 + 依分類)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products?available=true&category_id={{category_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api","v1","products"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "available", "value": "true" },
                { "key": "category_id", "value": "{{category_id}}" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Product Detail",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products/{{product_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","products","{{product_id}}"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Product Customizations",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products/{{product_id}}/customizations", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","products","{{product_id}}","customizations"] }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "[Admin] 分類管理",
      "description": "需要 admin_token。",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Category",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('category_id', String(json.data.id));",
                  "    console.log('category_id saved:', json.data.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/categories", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","categories"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"特調飲品\",\n  \"description\": \"三麗鷗聯名限定飲品系列\",\n  \"sort_order\": 1\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Category",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/categories/{{category_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","categories","{{category_id}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"限定特調\",\n  \"sort_order\": 2,\n  \"is_active\": true\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Category",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/categories/{{category_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","categories","{{category_id}}"] }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "[Admin] 商品管理",
      "description": "需要 admin_token。建立商品後可新增客製化選項（杯型/冰量/甜度/加料）。",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Product",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('product_id', String(json.data.id));",
                  "    console.log('product_id saved:', json.data.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","products"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"category_id\": {{category_id}},\n  \"name\": \"Hello Kitty 草莓拿鐵\",\n  \"description\": \"以草莓糖漿打造的粉紅色系拿鐵，附Hello Kitty造型拉花\",\n  \"price\": 120,\n  \"image_url\": \"\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Product",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products/{{product_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","products","{{product_id}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"price\": 130,\n  \"description\": \"以草莓糖漿打造的粉紅色系拿鐵，附Hello Kitty造型拉花（更新版）\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Set Availability: 下架",
